CustomField.description: Defines the Record ID of the Entity that the Portal Specific Setting applies. If there is no Portal Specific Setting defined for an Entity, the values in the default setting will be used.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines the Record ID of the Entity that the Portal Specific Setting applies. If there is no Portal Specific Setting defined for an Entity, the values in the default setting will be used.
